<br>
If you sit on the other side, the throne, the pit area or anywhere else you will get every wanderer, and not see pops till you get whacked. Idea is to sit and conserve (once KEI wears out . . . whatever you do DO NOT GIVE UP THE ROOM FOR ANY REASON. If you do you will lose the camp - It is fought over like rabid dogs over a fresh bone. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=aumnyder>Aumnyder</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 20<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(10/15/03 2:13 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm45.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=98.topic&index=28>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: shards</span><hr size=1> Quote: <br>
