<br>
I got extremely lucky.. first day there, I got one shard in the first half hour. Camped about four hours that day. Second day there, camped about four hours again, managed to get one just before I left.  The third day, I got two shards in a half hour I think. Yeah. Crazy. All in all it wasn't a huge time sink.<br>
<br>
Another thing I enjoyed was the learning - it was still pretty good for AA ... It was also a fun time spent with friends, getting our techniques down pat. As well, I managed to find a fair number of other spells, including one I needed - Banishment of Shadows.<br>
<br>
Just stick with it, and try to see it as an opportunity to learn.<br>
